query:
INSERT INTO
                    bms_bandwidth_results (
                        provider_id,
                        bms_job_id,
                        url_tested,
                        routing_key,
                        worker_count,
                        status
                    )
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, 'Pending')
               RETURNING
                    id,
                    provider_id,
                    bms_job_id,
                    url_tested,
                    routing_key,
                    worker_count,
                    status,
                    ping_avg_ms,
                    head_avg_ms,
                    ttfb_ms,
                    download_speed_mbps,
                    created_at,
                    completed_at
